2026-02-26T17:41:56Z | 8ac5eb46f5492ab6385b4edc9ff53976544d7db1 | Refactor admin mutations

Made PlanDialog, AppSettingsCard, AuthFlowSettingsCard, FeatureSettingsCard, NotificationTemplatesManager, UsersTab to use the admin deferred mutations flow. Introduced and wired new defer functions (deferUpdatePlan, deferCreatePlan, deferUpdateSettings, deferUpdateNotificationTemplate, etc.), replaced direct mutations with governance-queued changes, and added user-focused deferred mutations (update, toggle, role changes). Updated related UI to reflect queued changes and provide consistent admin governance across landing, web, and app surfaces.

